stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Scheduled: Practice booked
    Scheduled --> NotificationSent: 12-24h before
    NotificationSent --> Responded: User taps emoji
    NotificationSent --> Skipped: User taps Skip
    NotificationSent --> Reminded: 4h passed no response
    Reminded --> Responded: User taps emoji
    Reminded --> Skipped: User taps Skip
    Reminded --> Expired: Practice started
    Responded --> WithText: User adds description
    Responded --> Complete: No text added
    WithText --> Complete: Text saved
    Skipped --> Complete: Recorded as skipped
    Expired --> Complete: Recorded as no_response
    Complete --> [*]
